snippet.textDisplay:
Awesome song!! But little disappointed with the fact that English lyrics overpowered totally in the final segment. I still don't get it - why are these Indian composers so obsessed with having English lines? Coke studio is supposed to focus on core indian tunes and use western elements to enhance it,isn't it? or is it just opposite?

Anyhow loved the song and the whole arrangement, felt really good listening to it, a great creative effort from Hash Kale & team!
